/*--------------------------------*- Choupo -*--------------------------------*\
  rigorous column demo: a C3-C6 hydrocarbon column with TWO feeds and TWO side draws.
  Ideal (Raoult); the wide, well-separated volatilities (propane 231 K ->
  n-hexane 342 K) let each product isolate one component.
\*---------------------------------------------------------------------------*/
components       ( propane  nButane  nPentane  nHexane );
activityModel    { model  ideal; }
equationOfState  { model  idealGas; }
